":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:29:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>不過實際上我唔太意外,成單案嘅手法基本都暗示晒出黎,犯案嘅必定係係體育館做預備工作嘅人<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都苟延殘喘咁揀左次夜長,可惜都係要面對現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢犯案條䌫繩又直接放係網球場 唔套返好佢<br />\n手扣人地死左又唔除落黎收埋佢 <br />\n我覺得太唔小心了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw斬美逃跑嗰陣幾好睇"},{"pid":"618343d45c0ffad415885aabb19240c3196be63f","tid":417461,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:31:53.000Z","msg":"不過就算東条係兇手,我都係咁鍾意佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n處刑果種惡趣味嘅結局已經習慣左,但開頭成班人叫佢辭職我都係唔小心笑左,真係好仆街<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n心機算盡,連審判後都未放棄過要利用其他人繼續生存落去<br />\n我覺得佢果個由始至終都係為自己嘅身份(超高校級女僕)拼命嘅姿態實在太型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n就連死果個畫面都係咁美麗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b6361d0a269020823ca7b3a6371025dd0613ee52","tid":417461,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:38:31.000Z","msg":"哩一章同第一章比就無得比架啦,差太遠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n兇手同死者一開始就有晒共識同覺悟,所以就算死左我都相對無咁鬱悶<br />\n<br />\n不過原本睇到翻炒動機影片就覺得無聊,但之後換左片又覺得幾有趣<br />\n結果東条係唔好彩收到自己條片...<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />好囉屌你<br />\n<br />\n星果條片又係極仆街,諗都無諗過咁撚賤<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n不過我覺得最大嘅不合理之處都係確定身份嘅果塊手套碎布<br />\n就算按佢地所講無其他手套可以用,佢是但搵塊布黎剎車都可以掛...我唔覺得東条計到咁盡會miss 左哩個咁明顯嘅問題<br />\n<br />\n同埋東条之所以可以一個係體育館做預備工作,好大程度係因為夜長同夢野比權太捉走左<br />\n咁如果王馬無做到哩件事,東条哩個計劃由一開始就會有返咁上下阻滯<br />\n雖然佢有哩個意圖要呃走果兩條友都唔係咩大問題嘅....<br />\n<br />\nanyway, 期待第三章<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d7ba46148ebade740a32fd6e2eeda83bec8b2dd","tid":417461,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:40:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>不過實際上我唔太意外,成單案嘅手法基本都暗示晒出黎,犯案嘅必定係係體育館做預備工作嘅人<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都苟延殘喘咁揀左次夜長,可惜都係要面對現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢犯案條䌫繩又直接放係網球場 唔套返好佢<br />\n手扣人地死左又唔除落黎收埋佢 <br />\n我覺得太唔小心了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw斬美逃跑嗰陣幾好睇</blockquote><br />\n真係太多因為唔小心而比人定罪嘅地方,所以我覺得推理果段無第一章咁神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然天網恢恢,疏而不漏,就算小心左可能都會出錯嘅..."},{"pid":"4ee5166387e6ca179e1f7a3bc853e59a68db0eba","tid":417461,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:46:26.000Z","msg":"Btw 春川都型到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原本就覺得佢一定係戰鬥派,估唔到係暗殺者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"78b146e75e200acecdc5a38d338cef0f265cecd1","tid":417461,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:52:53.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>不過實際上我唔太意外,成單案嘅手法基本都暗示晒出黎,犯案嘅必定係係體育館做預備工作嘅人<br />\n<br />\n雖然我都苟延殘喘咁揀左次夜長,可惜都係要面對現實<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n佢犯案條䌫繩又直接放係網球場 唔套返好佢<br />\n手扣人地死左又唔除落黎收埋佢 <br />\n我覺得太唔小心了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nbtw斬美逃跑嗰陣幾好睇</blockquote><br />\n真係太多因為唔小心而比人定罪嘅地方,所以我覺得推理果段無第一章咁神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n當然天網恢恢,疏而不漏,就算小心左可能都會出錯嘅...</blockquote><br />\n轉子嘅合氣道都比唔上權太嘅蠻力<br />\n權太嘅蠻力又比唔上女僕嘅萬能<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n 斬美可能就係最好打嘅人物 最衰太不小心<br />\n而且星想死直接留段證據 話比大家知要自願犧牲 再由斬美先斬後奏咪得囉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過黑白熊一定會阻住哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0d4ef58132736b8e52f7a25b30d5f3b1ba9c90d1","tid":417461,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:53:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Btw 春川都型到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原本就覺得佢一定係戰鬥派,估唔到係暗殺者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n第三章就可以感受到佢嘅可愛<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"132756b0727314776069243fa6674255eede2733","tid":417461,"uid":139613,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:55:40.000Z","msg":"Btw睇到斬美同入間得bra嗰陣有冇彈驚"},{"pid":"0f45b36a4330e479b65c562bcc2fa6bc3e5d9977","tid":417461,"uid":31242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T03:57:09.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Btw睇到斬美同入間得bra嗰陣有冇彈驚</blockquote><br />\n點會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />me 係以欣賞藝術嘅方法睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n東条對腳真係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8ffb6e4e272b1996ea229c5c418ffb96cad70cbe","tid":417461,"uid":40078,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T04:03:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>Btw 春川都型到爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n原本就覺得佢一定係戰鬥派,估唔到係暗殺者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n春川黑臉嗰陣真係好型<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7568c67c928b5effe568eb7f14e9e6eb013c3a6d","tid"